features: Powered by NVIDIA Turing with 1408 CUDA Cores and overclocked-selected 6GB GDDR6 memory
Supports up-to 4 Monitors with DisplayPort 1. 4 and HDMI 2. 0. Recommended PSU : 450W
Full Cooling Control with DirectCU II with patented Wing-Blade Fans to increase airflow through the heatsink while ASUS FanConnect II provides dual 4-pin GPU-controlled PWM fan headers
ASUS Aura Sync RGB lighting features a nearly endless spectrum of colors with the ability to synchronize effects across an ever-expanding ecosystem of Aura Sync enabled products
GPU Tweak II makes monitoring performance and streaming in real time easier than ever, and includes additional software like Game Booster, XSplit Gamecaster, WTFast and QuantumCloud
description: Powered by NVIDIA Turing, the ROG Strix GTX 1660 SUPER is the perfect blend of price, performance and style. The overclocked-selected 6GB GDDR6 memory and 1408 CUDA Cores are cooled by DirectCU II and ASUS FanConnect II, while Aura Sync RGB lighting on the shroud delivers a distinctive, customized look.
